nodes.text: The Battle of Ansett Island was a battle that the First Order took part in on Ansett Island sometime before the mission to Kef Bir. During the battle, the stormtrooper designated as TZ-1719 and the rest of her company laid down their weapons when ordered to fire on civilians. They deserted and settled on the ocean moon Kef Bir. After the battle, TZ-1719 took on the name Jannah.
